  <title>case:disposition-to-casesum:disposition <lnpid>id-UK03-27423</lnpid></title>
  <body>
   <section>
     <p>
       <sourcexml>case:disposition</sourcexml> becomes
       <targetxml>casesum:disposition/p/text</targetxml>.
       
<pre>
&lt;DIGESTDOC&gt;
  &lt;dig:body&gt;
    &lt;level&gt;
      &lt;bodytext&gt;
        &lt;case:embeddedcase&gt;
          &lt;case:content&gt;
            &lt;case:judgments&gt;
              &lt;case:disposition&gt;His Lordship refused to order a sale. He ordered that
                                the husband, so long as he remained in possession, should pay the
                                wife £5 a week. No order was made as to costs.
              &lt;/case:disposition&gt;
            &lt;/case:judgments&gt;
          &lt;/case:content&gt;
        &lt;/case:embeddedcase&gt;
      &lt;/bodytext&gt;
    &lt;/level&gt;
  &lt;/dig:body&gt;
&lt;/DIGESTDOC&gt;

<b>Becomes</b>
&lt;casedigest:casedigest&gt;
  &lt;casedigest:body&gt;
    &lt;section&gt;
      &lt;bodytext&gt;
        &lt;courtcase:caseexcerpt&gt;
          &lt;courtcase:body&gt;
            &lt;courtcase:opinions&gt;
              &lt;casesum:disposition&gt;
                &lt;p&gt;
                  &lt;text&gt;
                        His Lordship refused to order a sale. He ordered that
                        the husband, so long as he remained in possession, should pay the
                        wife £5 a week. No order was made as to costs.
                  &lt;/text&gt;
                &lt;/p&gt;
              &lt;/casesum:disposition&gt;
            &lt;/courtcase:opinions&gt;
          &lt;/courtcase:body&gt;
        &lt;/courtcase:caseexcerpt&gt;
      &lt;/bodytext&gt;
    &lt;/section&gt;
  &lt;/casedigest:body&gt;  
&lt;/casedigest:casedigest&gt;
</pre> 
       <note>If
         <sourcexml>case:disposition</sourcexml> is child of <sourcexml>case:headnote</sourcexml>
         element then the full mappings from Rosetta to NL are as follows:<ul>
           <li><sourcexml>Case:headnote/case:disposition</sourcexml> becomes
             <targetxml>courtcase:head/casesum:summaries/casesum:disposition</targetxml>.</li>
         </ul>
       </note>
       <pre>
<![CDATA[
<DIGESTDOC>
    <dig:body>
        <level>
            <bodytext>
                <case:embeddedcase>
                    <case:headnote>
                        <case:disposition>
                            <p>
                                <text>The claimants' appeal was dismissed.</text>
                            </p>
                        </case:disposition>
                    </case:headnote>
                </case:embeddedcase>
            </bodytext>
        </level>
    </dig:body>
</DIGESTDOC>
]]>
<b>Becomes</b>
